=== Standards support ===
Support for [[Rainbow Books|Rainbow book]] standards:
* Red book: [[Compact Disc Digital Audio|CD-DA]]
* Yellow book: [[CD-ROM]]
* Orange book: [[CD-R]] and [[CD-RW]]
* [[White Book (CD standard)|White book]]: [[Video CD|VCD]] and [[Super Video CD|SVCD]]
* [[Blue Book (CD standard)|Blue book]]: [[Enhanced CD|E-CD]]
* Beige book: [[Photo CD|PCD]]
* [[Green Book (CD standard)|Green book]]: [[Philips CD-i|CD-i]] discs
* Purple book: [[Double-density compact disc|DDCD]]
* Scarlet book: [[Super Audio CD|SACD]]

